POST Req
            req -> json() -> route() -> res

Environments
    ```
    console.log(`NODE_ENV ${process.env.NODE_ENV}`);
    console.log(`Application ${app.get('env')}`);
    if (app.get('env') === 'development') {
        app.use(morgan('dev'));
    }
    ```    

